name: Archer Jungle Survival
description:
Step into a beautiful open Animals world and teeming with life and your experience of hunting, the jungle is full of from majestic deer and awe-inspiring bison, down to the countless birds, critters, and insects of the wilderness.

Features:
● Amazing graphics and prehistoric sceneries
● True life hunting experience
● Realistic animated animals
● Many thrilling missions with different number of animals
